Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在被星光照射的頂屋裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.90,0:00:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨自一人聆聽著天空的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.55,0:00:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用玻璃的繃帶遮住眼睛行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是孤獨的馬戲團孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.85,0:00:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤身一人的悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,震動的繃帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.87,0:00:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撼動著心靈……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.35,0:01:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用溫柔的眼神期待與某人的相會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.05,0:01:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我耳邊細語「請留在我身邊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.27,0:01:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Silent Voice
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.32,0:01:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡違規的離開亞加瑪了\n但這是因為在加拉帕基地戰爭中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.89,0:01:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和古利明的高性能戰機戰鬥時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.42,0:01:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查和莫迪他們做的太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.04,0:01:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥中被當成盾牌誰也會討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.10,0:01:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此戰爭結束後,露卡離開了亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.05,0:01:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十話 藍色部隊 前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.70,0:02:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是喀爾達亞城嗎?\n就放在這裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.52,0:02:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到哈曼是想控制新吉翁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.00,0:02:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據吉翁軍訓\n以狄根薩比為首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.97,0:03:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙世紀65年\n吉翁公國誕生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.46,0:03:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在79年一連串戰爭爆發中,狄根薩比也死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.44,0:03:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的死意味著什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.80,0:03:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是薩克坦克,而且...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.17,0:03:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來迎接我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.42,0:03:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是新吉翁的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.93,0:03:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但為何在這種地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.55,0:03:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道,只不過可能用得到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.44,0:04:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自由城市\n為何要出示身份證明?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.65,0:04:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏不再是以往的喀爾達亞城\n真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.49,0:04:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為非洲獨立游擊隊的活躍\n所以為了慎防間諜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.29,0:04:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那和我無關\n不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.34,0:04:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是間諜\n間諜會說自己是間諜嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.94,0:04:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有朋友在此\n那說出那個人的名子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.89,0:04:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是...\n叫什麼名子阿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.09,0:04:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我...\n別想砌詞狡辯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.59,0:04:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,親愛的,你來的真慢阿\n我忘了帶身份證不知怎麼辦 對不起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.84,0:04:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你慎重點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.07,0:04:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起傑尼先生,這女人...\n傑尼,來說清楚我們的關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.28,0:04:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用在隱瞞,說出來吧\n瑪莉安,是你不好 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.73,0:04:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她由我來保證,她是新收的學生\n但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.45,0:04:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我太可惡了,對不起,瑪莉安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.50,0:04:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.25,0:05:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是相信傑尼先生的話\n只不過那是第幾個女人? 怎麼知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.38,0:05:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝你的幫忙\n我也要感謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.44,0:05:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正在找藝術靈感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.18,0:05:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才幫你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.69,0:05:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,你本身就是藝術的化身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.36,0:05:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等,你想要我脫衣服嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.09,0:05:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是只有裸體才是藝術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.86,0:05:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是普通人...\n我不是普通人,是天才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.03,0:05:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真敢說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我來\n去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.56,0:05:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到為白種人專用的地方\n白種人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.88,0:05:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這城市的人特別為我們\n歐洲人所準備的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.37,0:05:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不肯,我要洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.73,0:05:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡不在工作已經堆積如山\n別在我身邊呱呱叫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.23,0:05:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡不在是比查的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.27,0:05:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個我知道\n都是因為你這樣對露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.68,0:06:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我連這個小孩也要照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.57,0:06:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把人家說的這麼壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.27,0:06:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你自己也覺得露卡不在比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.50,0:06:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒...沒這回事!\n水阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.38,0:06:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道的\n我是代替你趕走露卡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.20,0:06:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強詞奪理\n不是水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.90,0:06:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然,怎麼會是水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.72,0:06:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手阿\n住手,波蕾,關掉它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.74,0:06:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇,身體油淋淋的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.97,0:06:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冠武,洗達,快關掉油掣\n什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.69,0:06:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關掣,關總掣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.00,0:06:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去\n在追到敵人前已經用完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.17,0:06:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先清理地面濕滑在繼續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.12,0:06:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.44,0:06:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何清洗會用油的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.31,0:06:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為在地球時才會清洗砂粒\n找地方補給
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.55,0:07:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是露卡的工作\n你在諷刺嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.11,0:07:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是,只是的確很讓人困惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.22,0:07:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏嗎?\n走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.93,0:07:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你果然有不軌企圖\n是的話你會怎麼做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.40,0:07:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別以為我和那些女人一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.26,0:07:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真受不了你的倔強\n放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.48,0:07:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這地方有升降機?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.68,0:07:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下面有更有趣的東西\n有趣的東西..?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.53,0:07:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要\n波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.21,0:07:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,不去喀爾達亞嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.02,0:07:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想補給,但會阻延行程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.47,0:07:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去補給吧\n這樣也可以追上我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.99,0:07:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,但是呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.44,0:08:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行...捷度\n抓到了,幫你徹底弄乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.60,0:08:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.89,0:08:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾\n為何不能去喀爾達亞?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.67,0:08:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為露卡她...\n露卡怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.65,0:08:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼,沒什麼\n露卡在那裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.07,0:08:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道\n艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.78,0:08:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度..\n我去補給燃油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.44,0:08:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度\n我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.24,0:08:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊,幫我駕駛運輸機\n好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.56,0:08:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣好嗎?艦長\n補充是你管理的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.33,0:08:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別跟丟了\n知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.58,0:08:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼?\n想丟下我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.98,0:08:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這樣也算女人嗎?\n出發,出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.26,0:09:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種地方真的有地下城嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.10,0:09:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是入口嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.39,0:09:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然如他們所說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.85,0:09:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我為什麼非遵照他所說不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.74,0:09:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這樣的白種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.83,0:09:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要靠樣貌就能進入喀爾達亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.81,0:09:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了地下城後就探查管理部\n知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.17,0:09:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何要這樣做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.41,0:09:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是非洲獨立游擊隊藍部隊\n藍部隊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.13,0:09:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們現在為了取回被白種人\n控制的喀爾達亞而戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.97,0:09:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你要去地下城調查管制部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.01,0:10:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功後\n我們才相信你是新吉翁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.28,0:10:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.95,0:10:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,要忍耐\n我非回宇宙不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.45,0:10:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.50,0:10:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是露卡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.68,0:10:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照舊,你呢?\n相同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.91,0:10:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直和懷舊電影一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.34,0:10:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使科技怎麼進步\n人所追求的也是一樣,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.21,0:10:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新人類也不例外\n我也這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.67,0:10:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類所需要的就像你的美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.90,0:10:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和人之間的愛\n現在的你正渴求著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.97,0:10:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也這麼想...\n對阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.41,0:11:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那臭男人在對露卡做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.68,0:11:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡你旅途累了,飯後慢慢休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.48,0:11:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這好色鬼!\n不要...古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.43,0:11:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的朋友嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.36,0:11:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑尼先生,不要隨便開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.03,0:11:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡小姐,別這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.52,0:11:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們能在此相見\n是神的指引,是我們的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.38,0:11:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真敢說\n露卡小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.57,0:11:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收斂點,她被你嚇怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.57,0:11:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真有膽,混帳!\n住手,古利明,傑尼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.03,0:11:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好硬的臉..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.73,0:11:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別以為我是藝術家就小看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.84,0:11:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,和我走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.31,0:12:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,疑,去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.85,0:12:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好慢,古利明能信賴嗎?\n他已經逃走了,迪特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.96,0:12:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別急\n艾路,古利明才剛進入城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.74,0:12:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓在沙漠撿到的宇宙人加入隊伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.10,0:12:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對是錯誤的決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.81,0:12:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明是新吉翁的軍官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.98,0:12:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收納他就能左右新吉翁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.59,0:12:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明對我們很有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.88,0:12:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長,我們非洲獨立游擊隊員\n是留著賈帝普的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.08,0:12:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藍部隊並不是虛有其表的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.35,0:12:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賈帝普.耶辛是發起非洲獨立的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.16,0:13:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賈帝普的事我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.09,0:13:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是古利明是白種人的間諜怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.71,0:13:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一眼就認出我們薩克型號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.74,0:13:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,他不是普通人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.77,0:13:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才相信他是新吉翁的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.53,0:13:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且若是我們要鎮壓喀爾達亞\n一定要地下城的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.60,0:13:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...\n隊長,據偵查隊報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.55,0:13:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現往喀爾達亞的飛行物體\n什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.79,0:13:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,資料顯示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.42,0:13:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從路線上看來不是賈帝普.耶辛的軍隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.54,0:13:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是來救援那男人的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.30,0:13:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對,若是這樣不會這麼迅速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.28,0:13:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去迎擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在他們來到我軍陣地\n前後進攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.71,0:13:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道\n艾路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.09,0:13:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發動坦克引擎\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.78,0:13:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黏黏的好噁心\n又不能用水,沒辦法阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.98,0:13:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要洗澡...\n別黏著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.09,0:14:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再吵什麼?有什麼事嗎?\n喀爾達亞是在盆地上面哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.22,0:14:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有奇怪的感覺\n因為滿身的油污吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.25,0:14:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對\n阿!是城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.40,0:14:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼?\n不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.46,0:14:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是從喀爾達亞來的嗎?\n沒聽說會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.32,0:14:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是從喀爾達亞的人嗎?\n我不是敵人,我不是來戰鬥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.13,0:14:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.86,0:14:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓你碰到喀爾達亞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.41,0:14:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說什麼?\n捷度你還不明白嗎?是敵人阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.26,0:14:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發射迫擊炮,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.52,0:14:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉,伊萊\n沒事,只是漆油掉了些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.37,0:14:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來非戰不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.73,0:15:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直不自量力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.13,0:15:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機槍… 再派一輛機過來\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.19,0:15:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算沒有機槍也可以收拾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.68,0:15:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掉下去了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.11,0:15:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!\n艾莉,上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.50,0:15:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,怎樣?\n沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.31,0:15:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想喘口氣也不能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.90,0:15:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是什麼人?吉翁嗎?新吉翁嗎?\n不是那些無聊人,我是藍部隊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.90,0:15:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想聽聽你的心意,露卡小姐\n是你任意出現在我身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.19,0:15:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是連新吉翁也能支配的男人\n只要你在我身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.66,0:16:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人不是這麼簡單的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.78,0:16:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼?是戰鬥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.89,0:16:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.31,0:16:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MS在戰鬥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.99,0:16:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藍部隊在戰鬥,敵人是誰?\n不是認真的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.87,0:16:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追求女人途中被戰事所吸引
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.73,0:16:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事是最大禁忌\n露...露卡小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.39,0:16:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.97,0:16:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.45,0:16:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然是舊式但也不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.65,0:16:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.01,0:16:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了,在右邊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.21,0:16:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧!\n捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.65,0:16:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀,激光槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.76,0:17:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手法好強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.82,0:17:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害\n他只是普通人為何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.26,0:17:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去了!以賈帝普之血之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.21,0:17:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.49,0:17:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,危險啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.99,0:17:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看..\n不只一輛戰機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.71,0:17:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾路,只有你一個太勉強了\n看清楚敵人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.73,0:17:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長,射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.63,0:17:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那MS去了哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.82,0:17:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希斯有危險\n什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.12,0:17:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以這個薩克的改裝程式\n應該可以跳到那各高度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.78,0:18:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那各應該是高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.54,0:18:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是舊式戰機吧\n但內部不同是經過改裝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.81,0:18:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有激光槍真難應付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.84,0:18:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非洲獨立游擊隊來了\n逃到地下城就安全了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.88,0:18:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要油就毫不知恥的要來了\n果然沒有我還是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.58,0:18:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真認真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.16,0:18:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡小姐\n不要到地下城,是很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.22,0:18:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要\n等賈帝斯大軍一到,這裏會成為戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.17,0:18:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想安慰被嚇到的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.41,0:18:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡,你也寂寞吧,你的身影告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.84,0:18:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個人真是\n別看輕女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.97,0:19:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛是露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.94,0:19:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿到了...這樣的話!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.03,0:19:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去會追到\n飛進那巖堆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.39,0:19:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想藉此躲藏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.79,0:19:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣進攻\n準備好 3, 2, 1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.81,0:19:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.76,0:19:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!\n捷度呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.02,0:19:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是Z高達,亞加瑪那些傢伙\n竟然派露卡去當間諜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.28,0:20:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我不會讓藍部隊被打敗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.70,0:20:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不會讓捷度被打敗的\n什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.51,0:20:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了非洲自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.39,0:20:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種感覺是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.29,0:20:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會讓他打敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.66,0:20:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟避開了那個飛彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.79,0:20:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度\n艾路被打敗了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.49,0:20:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉,伊萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.47,0:20:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度  沒事吧?\n嗯,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.42,0:20:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.04,0:20:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是MS的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.68,0:20:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.34,0:20:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.84,0:21:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明?明白了,我們撤退\n敵人應該沒有能飛的MS了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.26,0:21:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高達隊撤退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.98,0:21:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害我白擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.51,0:21:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來襲的MS究竟是什麼\n還有那種感覺...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.28,0:21:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,露卡在喀爾達亞城\n你感覺到露卡嗎? 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.86,0:21:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,將戰機藏在城附近\n再步行進入喀爾達亞城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.72,0:21:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡一定是降落在這附近的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.41,0:21:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了,就這麼辦\n瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.30,0:21:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪特,振作點,我還要像你道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.49,0:21:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊,艾路\n你是勇敢的戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.51,0:22:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.58,0:22:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再說了,迪特\n會加重傷勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.34,0:22:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我說吧\n多謝你了,古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.68,0:22:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是吉翁的軍隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.13,0:22:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明,我最後請求你\n為了藍部隊的名譽給我戰鬥吧,古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.57,0:22:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了\n拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.30,0:22:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪特\n迪特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.30,0:22:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成百 成萬 上億的繁星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.49,0:22:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何只是閃耀而已 展示你言語的能力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.55,0:23:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我也能不回頭地 讓心靈出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.70,0:23:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能把多如繁星的生命儲存的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.65,0:23:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把整個銀河也化作光芒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.35,0:23:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,化作緊握在掌心的 生命的重量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.32,0:23:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我仍未能看見宇宙的路標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.22,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手掌觸摸著一千萬年的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.46,0:23:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無精打采的話就不知道是選擇露 還是選擇核心戰機了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.97,0:23:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 不能再說這種話了
